<h2 id="how-does-wtc-make-money">How does WTC make money?</h2>

<p>WTC makes its money from selling Google ads. For this to be effective, they need to maintain a competitive amount of recent and relevant content on their website. This allows their page to rank highly in searches, bringing traffic to their site, and increasing follow-through on the ads that WTC features.</p>

<div class="customer-quote-block" style="padding-left:5%;padding-right:15%">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <div class="customer-quote p-10">"Revenue has basically gone straight up since the Nyckel integration."</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 pl-0">
